features: [Quality Paulownia Wood] Our floating shelves are crafted from high-quality and durable paulownia wood, known for its exceptional strength, lightness, and resistance to cracking, moisture, decay, and abrasion. Unlike pine wood, which is prone to moisture damage, mildew, and cracking, our paulownia shelves offer long-lasting performance even in the bathroom.

[Practical Storage Solution] Our bathroom storage cabinet features a convenient wire storage basket, ideal for storing extra toilet paper or other essentials. It is easy to assemble and remarkably lightweight. Place it on the over toilet tank, and it can comfortably hold up to 3 toilet paper rolls.

[Elegant Home Decor] Add a touch of elegance to any interior style with our floating shelves. Whether your space follows a modern, traditional, rustic, or industrial theme, these shelves seamlessly blend in. They bring a sense of nature and harmony to modern styles and a touch of wholeness to retro-rustic settings. Great for organizing books, collectibles, plants, trophies, and more on your wall.

[Easy to Install] Our package includes everything you need for quick and easy installation: a clear installation guide, 2 shelf boards with metal guardrails, 1 shelf board with a storage basket, and the necessary hardware. Simply follow the instructions, and within minutes, your shelves will be securely mounted, transforming your wall into a functional storage space. Shelf dimensions: 16" L x 6" W.

[After Sale Service] RYOFOBETTO provides friendly customer service, and we respect the needs of our clients. Please do not hesitate to contact us if you are having problems with the product or if you have any questions about it.

reviews.reviewText: These are easy to install, well-made, and very useful. All 3 are up and look great in my bathroom!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice looking shelves
reviews.reviewText: I really like these. They added a nice decorative touch for the much needed storage in my bathroom. I like that they have the bar to keep things from falling off and the towel bar.I do wish that they had predrilled holes in the wood but the wood is soft and easy to put the screws in. I don't know what type of wood it is, but it is very light. It seems very sturdy. It was easy to install. I recommend these.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Great looking in our bathroom and a nice set of 3 for a good price. They were a little challenging putting together since none of the screws had pilot holes. They didn’t hand flush to the wall with the provided screws so going to stop by Lowe’s tomorrow to get something that works better. Overall great shelves and value, just a little more work than expected

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars It's alright for the cost, but very cheap and flimsy
reviews.reviewText: Hung these in my bathroom, and I am constantly aware they can fall out of the wall with a slight tug. The anchors provided are very tough to work with. They take a lot of work to get into the wall, but if you work to hard at it or make the initial drill hole too big they will fall right out or push into the wall too far.Although it looks nice at a glance, the wood boards are very light, soft, and cheap feeling. I understand it's probably to allow the bars to be screwed in easily, but a nicer wood with pre-drilled holes would be preferable.I suppose you're getting what you pay for.
